        {
            "title": "印度據悉暫時排除對美國關稅展開報復 雙方保持非正式溝通渠道暢通",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 據一位知情官員透露，印度和美國目前保持非正式溝通渠道暢通，新德里暫無報復唐納德·川普對該南亞國家徵50%關稅的計畫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度商工部一位高級官員表示，雖然雙邊貿易協議談判被推遲，但兩國仍就國防和外交政策等關鍵問題繼續溝通。由於相關磋商並未公開，這位官員要求匿名。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該官員以特朗普政府官員與印度外交部和國防部高級代表本周的線上會談為例，說明兩國政府的關鍵部門在繼續接觸。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度商工部沒有回應尋求進一步信息的請求。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.Z6Si3x0qPWgGuL.hsJvog--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/165e5faf03d20570fc8e287377a78eab\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該官員表示，儘管下一輪談判的日期尚未確定，但新德里將與華盛頓一起繼續朝著達成雙邊貿易協議努力。原定於8月25日-29日抵達印度進行第六輪貿易談判的美國貿易代表團已推遲行程。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該官員表示，只有對等關稅和與俄羅斯石油採購有關的二級關稅都被廢除，兩國貿易協議才可能簽署。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題India Holds Informal US Talks, Rules Out Retaliation for Now (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Subhadip Sircar、Anup Roy.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9-%E9%9B%99%E6%96%B9%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E9%9D%9E%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%BA%9D%E9%80%9A%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93%E6%9A%A2%E9%80%9A-073219694.html",
